  "message": "chore(artifacts): refresh symbol_tiers_roadmap + symbol_universe_normalization + workload_api_wave_plan\n\nThree more conformance artifact rolls that had not yet flushed when\nthe previous artifact-refresh commit went out:\n\ntests/conformance/symbol_tiers_roadmap.v1.json (bd-2vv.10)\n  - generated_at advanced from 2026-04-26T01:15:06Z to\n    2026-04-26T17:37:04Z; roadmap_hash and total_symbols unchanged\n    (still 3996), so this is the regenerator picking up the same\n    universe but with a fresher timestamp + the cumulative effect\n    of the openat2 + faccessat2 + io_pgetevents + clone3 entries\n    on the support matrix that the wave plan references.\n\ntests/conformance/symbol_universe_normalization.v1.json (bd-2vv.9)\n  - Same universe_hash (80be34803bf6b987) and total_symbols (3996);\n    only the generated_at timestamp moves to 2026-04-26T17:37:05Z.\n\ntests/conformance/workload_api_wave_plan.v1.json\n  - support_matrix sha256 advances from\n    d9714dd1c9adcb7fda93d2e51f41089ebac0b6fad76ebe88b34ea3f0713466da\n    to\n    9cec31fd68f0dee107918b38c72b6123e31bea8b9399927af652d166d093c453\n    reflecting the newly-recorded ABI symbols.\n  - callthrough_census sha256 likewise advances.\n\nPure artifact refresh, no source touched.\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.7 (1M context) <noreply@anthropic.com>",
